             <lg> 
              <l>Tiny little secrets</l>
          <l>Get buried in the dirt,</l> 
          <l>And if they were dug up,</l>
          <l>Someone would probably get hurt,</l>
          <l>So leave them safely there,</l>
          <l>To rot amongst the leaves,</l>
          <l>Admiring instead,</l>
          <l>The truth in summer's green trees.</l>
         
                 
